  "body": "<p><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/8m7w413/Tool-Leveling-Banner.png\" alt=\"Tool Leveling\" width=\"822\" height=\"125\" /></p>\n\n<br>\n<hr>\n\n<p>how the mod works:</p>\n<!--<ul>\n    <li>craft the Tool Leveling Table</li>\n    <li>put an enchantable item in the big middle slot</li>\n    <li>place enough Enchanted Books in the left slots (by default at least 4 books)</li>\n    <li>bookshelfs around the table increase the chance of success</li>\n    <li>special items in the right slots will result in more and higher level enchantments</li>\n    <li>press \"Upgrade\"</li>\n</ul>-->\nWIP\n\n<hr>\n\n<h4>Recipe</h4>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/NWdBRSQ/recipe-v1-3-0.png\" alt=\"Recipe\" width=\"372\" height=\"186\" /></p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<h4>GUI</h4>\n<!--<p>The enchantment added to the tool will be picked from the books in the left slots.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/wN8yygv/gui-2-0-0-without-buttons.png\" alt=\"Tool Leveling Gui\" width=\"442\" height=\"480\" /></p>-->\nWIP\n\n<hr>\n\n<br>\n\nif you have any questions about the mod, or you want a few insights about upcoming features:\n<br>\nfeel free to join the Discord &nbsp;&nbsp;\n<a title=\"discord\" href=\"https://discord.gg/bhUaWhq\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n    <img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/VQ66pHN/Discord.png\" alt=\"Divider\" width=\"166\" height=\"32\" />\n</a>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;\n<a title=\"discord\" href=\"https://discord.gg/bhUaWhq\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">link</a>",
